{"tid":1672103,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人睇加泰係爭取緊獨立，其實外國人睇香港都係爭取緊獨立","createTime":"2019-10-24T02:08:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T02:50:25.000Z","uid":40250,"like":8,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0bdda585ff0b32e1793131751a89d071520f821d","tid":1672103,"uid":40250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:08:52.000Z","msg":"重點想講，中國控制大部份媒體，令好多根本未親身接觸示威者既人，單方面聽媒體所講，加泰係爭取緊獨立，情況同香港好相似<br />\n<br />\n當然，to be fair講句外媒都刻意抹黑同隱瞞，呢個都唔出奇。中國屌鬼佬偽善偽屌得無錯。<br />\n<br />\n不過，係偽善偽雙重標準又點撚樣呀中國？ 依家擺到明要反尻你，針對你，全球反中浪潮無人阻止到。雙重標準咪雙重標準，對付你呢種無賴，任何手段都可以用"},{"pid":"77de76961526a0ce56ed365d1bae0e32b5d79586","tid":1672103,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672101</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GCA3VqG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGCA3VqG.jpg&h=1b492863&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"95d576cbc0fa17022e3483005f5e9d46d19714b5","tid":1672103,"uid":279356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:14:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1yYtmny.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F1yYtmny.gif&h=db5af89f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d0874fab6abe181bc57d80fa37b9fddbe3407dea","tid":1672103,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:19:11.000Z","msg":"啱"},{"pid":"daf8dbacc328e3eb4b384be04536d0715d89721e","tid":1672103,"uid":110109,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77de76961526a0ce56ed365d1bae0e32b5d79586","tid":1672103,"uid":33930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T02:11:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>【SUCK／1026】長龍爆買日 - 黃店存貨壓力測試（2）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1672101\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1672101</a><br />\n<